            <p class="text-monica-light leading-relaxed" data-cms="story-family-text">
              As one of 10 children, I learned early the power of connection, communication, and finding your unique voice in a crowd. These childhood lessons shaped my passion for helping others discover their authentic selves and build meaningful relationships.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="journey-card group animate-slide-in-up">
            <div class="journey-icon-container">
              <div class="journey-icon">üíë</div>
              <div class="journey-icon-bg"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-monica-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-monica-teal transition-colors duration-300" data-cms="story-marriage-title">
              37 Years of Partnership
            </h3>
            <p class="text-monica-light leading-relaxed" data-cms="story-marriage-text">
              Married to my husband Steve for 37 years and raising three wonderful children, I understand the beautiful complexity of balancing personal dreams with family life. As a grandmother now, I cherish the wisdom that comes from life's transitions.
