              Finding My Purpose
            </h3>
            <p class="text-monica-light leading-relaxed" data-cms="story-purpose-text">
              In 2007, I founded New Steps Life Coaching after recognizing my calling to help others navigate life's challenges. What started as a personal mission has grown into a thriving practice that has transformed hundreds of lives.
